// ===BEGIN ICANN DOMAINS===
// Hermetic PSL subset for HostIndexResolverTest. Includes the minimum
// suffix surface needed by the data-provider matrix:
//   - apex + www on com / test / example
//   - multi-label TLDs co.uk + com.br
// Snapshot from https://publicsuffix.org/list/public_suffix_list.dat (MPL 2.0).

com
test

// example is reserved per RFC 2606; PSL lists it as an effective TLD for
// fixture / documentation domains.
example

// co.uk multi-label TLD (HOST-05).
uk
co.uk

// com.br multi-label TLD (HOST-05).
br
com.br

// ===END ICANN DOMAINS===
